{"tid":518087,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"梁游衝擊立會案 辯方質疑法庭偏幫控方 裁判官今直指辯方的說話對法庭不敬","createTime":"2018-01-03T03:27:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-03T04:12:43.000Z","uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"bc70a481f29a1ca197546d17f03cf47b38b6a7a0","tid":518087,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T03:27:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://drive.google.com/uc?id=1SnSq4RgZgUzGM3zXIRH8ZqjeGfILvyGk\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fuc%3Fid%3D1SnSq4RgZgUzGM3zXIRH8ZqjeGfILvyGk&h=a9a9630f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://drive.google.com/uc?id=1XTnlSUaDro1BrobBU_YeGpyyO8sO5CEj\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fuc%3Fid%3D1XTnlSUaDro1BrobBU_YeGpyyO8sO5CEj&h=7376aff3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://drive.google.com/uc?id=11YkvLvdgyLVLyfdwBpOU6RhwIVM3DahB\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fuc%3Fid%3D11YkvLvdgyLVLyfdwBpOU6RhwIVM3DahB&h=e95dd8e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n游蕙禎(左)及梁頌恆(右)續在九龍城法院應訊。(何全泰攝)<br />\n<br />\n青年新政前立法會議員游蕙禎及梁頌恆，涉嫌前年底衝擊立會會議室，兩人連同三名前議員助理鍾雪瑩、楊禮康及張子龍被控參與非法集結罪，及屬交替控罪的企圖強行進入罪，案件今日(2日)在九龍城法院續審。<br />\n<br />\n裁判官今就法律爭議裁決，指立法會已開會並發出特别許可，批准8名立法會人員出庭作供，故涉案的閉路電視片段亦可呈堂。<span style=\"color: red;\">此外，辯方早前質疑法庭偏幫控方，裁判官今直指辯方的說話對法庭不敬</span>，亦毫無根據，明言控辯雙方均有責任協助法庭處理法律爭議，故辯方說法並不恰當。<br />\n<br />\n辯方隨即作出陳詞，要求法庭裁定各被告兩項控罪表證不成立。辯方指，高等法院法官區慶祥於2016年10月中拒絕頒布臨時禁制令禁止游梁兩人再宣誓時，已預設立法會主席會於翌日容許二人再宣誓，故二人仍可繼續以議員身份行事，只是他們因建制派議員集體離場致流會等原因而一直未能再宣誓，而縱使人大於本案發生後釋法，也不影響區官之裁決。<br />\n<br />\n辯方續指，根據《議事規則》第45條，若議員因「行為極不檢點」而被趕走，該議員不可再出席該會議，惟游梁兩人案發當日進入會議廳後，立法會主席梁君彥並沒言明是引用哪一條條例趕他們離去，故控方沒證據證明他們不可再進入一號會議室，立法會保安亦是非法阻撓二人和其助理。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180102/mobile/bkn-20180102130955031-0102_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180102%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20180102130955031-0102_00822_001.html&d=3OAKf2X8IJcTyEPzQ8wmjRFQyUQXuyYblCT5RSyYNoQ%3D&h=f1582135\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180102/mobile/bkn-20180102130955031-0102_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"600bd61a89fd4b40b050adad1092ce14db9cd46c","tid":518087,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T03:39:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f3a4a957fc0479151931a34f825573f2780fa12","tid":518087,"uid":51469,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T03:42:30.000Z","msg":"講句咁既野有心靠害喎"},{"pid":"87a1634036fb010b0ca53d87600dc06f0d19dc09","tid":518087,"uid":51904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T03:44:27.000Z","msg":"得罪老爺<br />\n游B個菊花無喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4fd9801748f942265acdbadd500d824f09d3f2f","tid":518087,"uid":67065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T03:48:07.000Z","msg":"九成都打到終院嫁啦"},{"pid":"1c5ec238644c9975a9d11a38194e111cc4f6c34d","tid":518087,"uid":61279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T03:48:19.000Z","msg":"梁游 on9，搵個律師又係 on9 既<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5595b272183bcbfdeabd7efedd6b8d48c944cbcb","tid":518087,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T03:48:20.000Z","msg":"「法庭偏幫控方」呢句係上訴時講, <br />\n<br />\n唔係第一審時講架嘛<br />\n<br />\non <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72a543f672edd15fce98eebfa9e7bb4cd08b7edf","tid":518087,"uid":126283,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T03:49:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講句咁既野有